@startuml sd_SalaryItemService_getAll
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title SalaryItemService.getAll() - 获取工资项目列表

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "SalaryItemController" as Ctrl
participant "SalaryItemService" as Svc
participant "SalaryItemRepository" as Repo

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/salary-items
Ctrl -> Svc: getAll()
Svc -> Repo: findByActiveTrueOrderBySortOrder()
Repo --> Svc: List<SalaryItem>
note right of Svc : 仅返回active=true\n按sortOrder排序
Svc --> Ctrl: List<SalaryItem>\n[基本工资,年功工资,效益工资,...]
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse<List<SalaryItem>>
@enduml
